OL,3,CRamsey to take over as Cardiff City
OL,4,Csack manager Omer Riza mid relegation
OL,5,Cbattle
OL,7,FCardiff City FC has confirmed that
OL,8,FOmer Riza has been relieved of his
OL,9,Fduties as First Team Manager.
OL,11,FAaron Ramsey will lead the Club for
OL,12,Fthe remaining three games of the
OL,13,FChampionship season, beginning with
OL,14,FMonday's match at home to Oxford
OL,15,FUnited.
OL,17,FChris Gunter, Joe Ralls, Tom Hutton
OL,18,Fand Matthew Bloxham will join Ramsey
OL,19,Fin the technical area.
