OL,3,CRamsey to take over as Cardiff City
OL,4,Csack manager Omer Riza mid relegation
OL,5,Cbattle
OL,7,FIn a statement the club said "We'd
OL,8,Flike to thank Omer for his passion and
OL,9,Feffort during his time as Cardiff City
OL,10,Fmanager and wish him the very best for
OL,11,Fhis next steps in the game."
OL,13,FIt follows a 2-0 loss away to
OL,14,FSheffield United on Friday. The
OL,15,Fbluebirds sit in the relegation zone
OL,16,Fof the Championship and are facing
OL,17,Frelegation to League One.
OL,19,FIt would be the first time the club
OL,20,Fhave dropped to the third tier of the
OL,21,FEnglish Football League in 22 years.
