OL,4,Csack manager Omer Riza mid relegation
OL,5,Cbattle
OL,7,FReacting to the news, Phillip Nifield,
OL,8,Fboard member at the Cardiff City
OL,9,FSupporters Trust said "It's been a
OL,10,Flong time coming, the owners should've
OL,11,Facted months ago when the results
OL,12,Fstarted falling off a cliff.
OL,14,F"I think most fans would be glad to
OL,15,Fsee the back of Riza, he would come in
OL,16,Fthe top few of the worst managers I've
OL,17,Fseen in 60 years of supporting Cardiff
OL,18,FCity, he's up there right at the top."
