OL,7,FDespite Ramsey's lack of managerial
OL,8,Fexperience, Phillip Nifield was
OL,9,Fsupportive of the player's appointment.
OL,11,F"I know the fans will get behind
OL,12,FRamsey, but he's got a real tough
OL,13,Fjob." he said.
OL,15,F"I think probably we would've gone
OL,16,Fdown with Riza, we've got some hope
OL,17,Fnow that we might stay up.
